6. Laravel Charting Package: 
Creating charts is often a pain because of how you have to convert your data into what the charting library supports and each library is different. 
To help make this easier Erik Campobadal created a new Laravel chart package to create interactive charts.
https://laravel-news.com/laravel-charts

7. Laravel Passport : Easily setup your own OAuth2 server: Creating your own OAuth server can be difficult and Laravel 5.3 comes with a free optional package called Passport that is a full OAuth2 server that is ready to go in minutes.
https://laravel.com/docs/5.3/passport

8. Laravel Scout : Laravel Scout provides a simple, driver based solution for adding full-text search to your Eloquent models. 
https://laravel.com/docs/5.3/scout

9. Laravel Analytics v2 : For showing Google Analytics
https://laravel-news.com/laravel-analytics-v2

